The following category defines all milestones for webgen:


# Milestones #

* F: Ideas and todo items for future versions

  This milestone holds all ideas/todo items/requests which are implemented some
  time in the future.


## Implementation (open) ##

* what about fragment nodes? (created using a content processor, stored in cache, two webgen runs?)

* add easy method for getting all useable ContentConverters

* html validator should run after file written on .html files (configurable which files)

* allow blocks processor to use a filename as argument

* add ContentConverter which searches for wg-tagname="params" attributes and replaces them (see mail from andrew pietsch)


### Implementation (closed) ###





## Bugs (open) ##

* see mail from andrew pietsch regarding menu issues/'tapestry.apache.org' feature

* loggin level is assigned after plugin bundles gets loaded in cli.rb/website.rb -> need a hook or something


### Bugs (closed) ###




## Documentation (open) ##

* add glossary page

  source file name, output file name, canonical name, localized canonical name
  
* describe how the path patterns used in nodes_for_pattern work in section of naming of files.

* think about examples in documentation



### Documentation (closed) ###


